lenders.name: Alex Smith
lenders.occupational_info: Design Holiday has teamed up with Borgo Egnazia in Puglia, Italy to offer affordable and luxury vacations Whether you are seeking a cozy hotel room, a spacious town house or villa, or a calming resort and spa, Borgo Egnazia offers it.  Borgo Egnazia offers resort activities like an 18-hole golf course, a kid's club, water sports, and even cooking lessons. If you prefer the sea air and clear water of the Adriatic Sea, there are shores placed on the resort's property. Whether you are looking to book a family vacation, a weekend getaway or your honeymoon, Borgo Egnazia has something to offer you. If choosing to stay at the resort, you'll enjoy one of the 63 available rooms complete with modern conveniences and relaxing neutral tones.There are even interconnecting two bedroom suites available.  No matter what room you choose, you will get a picturesque view of the Adriatic Sea, the hilly Puglia terrain or the Borgo Egnazia's courtyard. For something more exclusive, try out one of the available three-bedroom villas that are spread throughout eight of the resort's buildings. Borgo Egnazia's villas offer you lavish attributes with space for the entire family.  The Borgo Egnazia villas come complete with terraced gardens, private pools and scenic balconies.For a better experience, you can also select one of the available town houses which have one to two bedrooms, a kitchenette, a sitting room along with a courtyard. The resort's village square is readily reachable from any of the rooms, town houses and villas, enabling you to benefit from the delightful restaurants and other activities.  When you've decided you're ready for a vacation far from your ordinary routine, reach out to the Design Holiday booking team and book your stay at the Borgo Egnazia.  If you'd like more information on booking your Borgo Egnazia stay, browse the website or call 01444 87 2200, today.
